  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\nwhen you open chat and use /send command with some amount (with comma i.e. 0,001) , enter amount - Send transaction with 0.00ETH instead of specified amount\r\n![oldamount](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34567518-47f1cccc-f16b-11e7-94fd-68a8d5498760.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nspecified amount is shown\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n0.00 ETH\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Use /faucet in Console chat (in order to get some ETH). After balance is updated, go to next step.\r\n- Start 1-1 chat\r\n-Type /send 0,0001 (for example) \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.11d512 (nightly 04.01)\r\n* Operating System: iOS, Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF 03:20 - \r\nhttps://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/7434230/sessions/18/?accessToken=8cTDnCTUoalcGAMAiMTQNUx3xVY\r\n",
